query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mc t) NoMergeJoin(mc t mi) NoMergeJoin(mc mi t mk) NoMergeJoin(mc mi mk t mi_idx) */ select count(*)
from movie_companies AS mc
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2005
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info_type_id = 8
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info_type_id = 101;
